const Form = () =>{
    return (
        <form action="">

            <label htmlFor="username" for='username'>
                Username: <input type="text" name="username"/>
            </label>
            
            <label htmlFor="">
                Password: <input type="text" />
            </label>

            <button>LOGIN</button>

        </form>
    )
}

export default Form
